= Tourniquet, a declarative dependency injection framework

Tourniquet provides a different way to write Ruby applications. It
helps developers write code that is modular and testable.

== Running the tests

Testing Tourniquet requires rspec:

    gem install rspec

Then to run the specs:

    rake spec:technical

